      "content": "i feel like the \"debate\" part is kind of a stretch though. like, the data on how much guns contribute to violence is pretty well documented in a lot of studies, right? isn't the idea that gun control works more of a factual reality than just an opinion? whereas the constitutional side is just people interpreting old text.",
